{"tid":512892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"now成人台強姦片太色情被投訴","createTime":"2017-12-29T03:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T06:48:10.000Z","uid":139228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa767d6cfe46bf1f30a877ee7964f6d599e1067b","tid":512892,"uid":139228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:32:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇人搵到呢條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n通訊局昨發新聞稿指，now寬頻電視今年3月7日晚上8時至9時，在旗下成人極品台播放電視節目<span style=\"color: red;\">《瀛事滾女科：強迫學生白書》</span>。局方接獲一名公眾人士投訴，指該節目播放真實強姦片段，內容過份暴力、令人不安及色情，並且會引人模仿，應該被禁止播放。<br />\n該節目講述一名身穿校服的女主角在街上被擄走、推上客貨車，然後被載到偏僻露天工地被人多次強姦。節目開首有文字顯示片中演員均為18歲以上，播放期間也有標題提醒觀眾啟動家長鎖碼裝置。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20171229&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20258571now成人台強姦片太色情通訊局嚴重警告\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171229%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20258571now%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%B0%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E7%89%87%E5%A4%AA%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E5%B1%80%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A&d=y7lpBltl%2FaEt7Gcm1OWnFtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=9e386784\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171229%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20258571now%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%B0%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6%E7%89%87%E5%A4%AA%E8%89%B2%E6%83%85%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E5%B1%80%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A&h=22870cf8\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20171229&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20258571now成人台強姦片太色情通訊局嚴重警告</a>"},{"pid":"9c0de5d9c79aa4380836bcfacda07f956d390c05","tid":512892,"uid":28163,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"嫖客投訴隻雞太咸濕"},{"pid":"f20d5b8c1ea53b2964c9ccaff8d4609e01a6bf94","tid":512892,"uid":133529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:41:29.000Z","msg":"正ON9